    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到克里斯传说~ 这是一款2D横板动作角色扮演游戏，你将扮演一个怀揣梦想的佣兵少年——克里斯，开启一段关于追逐自由和成长的冒险故事。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可爱的画风和世界观</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113840/extras/f1d7bf884ecaaa56285f096184f25e3c.poster.avif?t=1766683384\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113840/extras/f1d7bf884ecaaa56285f096184f25e3c.webm?t=1766683384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113840/extras/f1d7bf884ecaaa56285f096184f25e3c.mp4?t=1766683384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>简单上手又充满挑战的战斗系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113840/extras/165199742882e9df5367440fc387a152.poster.avif?t=1766683384\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113840/extras/165199742882e9df5367440fc387a152.webm?t=1766683384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113840/extras/165199742882e9df5367440fc387a152.mp4?t=1766683384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生动丰富的游戏剧情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113840/extras/f35a83ae5b239ddca386613d1181e0a9.poster.avif?t=1766683384\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://share